            <item xml:id="encampments">
               <!-- Encampments - in der Erfassungstabelle L -->
               <label>42 Encampments</label>
               <p>Lists the 42 encampments of the Israelites in 3 different years
                  <list>
                     <item>First arch: the encampments in the first year: 12</item>
                     <item>Second arch: the encampments in the second year: 21</item>
                     <item>Third arch: the encampments in the fortieth year: 9</item>
                  </list>             
              According to the flight of the Israelites described in Exodus, Numbers and Deuteronomy,
                  The journey to <placeName>Sinai</placeName> lasted for one year; departure from <placeName>Sinai</placeName> occurred at the beginning of the
                  second year; thus the names of the places of encampment are listed under the first arch; the
                  names of the places in the following 38 years under the second arch; the names of the places in
                  the last year (after <persName>Aaron</persName> died on <placeName>Mount Hor</placeName>) under the final arch.</p>
            </item>
            <item xml:id="encampments-a">
               <label>Type A</label>
               <p>
                     2 - 3 - 2 Columns
                  </p>
            </item>
            <item xml:id="encampments-b">
